export const Server = {
    endpoint : process.env.REACT_APP_ENDPOINT,
    project: process.env.REACT_APP_PROJECT,
    databaseID : process.env.REACT_APP_DATABASE_ID,
    adminID: process.env.REACT_APP_ADMIN_ID,
    customerID: process.env.REACT_APP_CUSTOMER_ID,
    orderID: process.env.REACT_APP_ORDER_ID,
    apiProductID: process.env.REACT_APP_API_PRODUCT_ID,
    dashboardDataID: process.env.REACT_APP_DASHBOARD_DATA_ID,
    apiRequestID: process.env.REACT_APP_API_REQUEST_ID,
    dataID: process.env.REACT_APP_DATA_ID
}
